{"type":"message","id":"f06d46c4","parentId":"40ae74f1","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:15:02.861Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:0bb637bb-765d-4c8a-b721-260619faf16f Tobias Task Watchdog] Run the Tobias task watchdog. Read C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\README.md for context. Execute python C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\watchdog.py, inspect its JSON output, and follow this rule strictly: if notifications is empty, reply with exactly NO_REPLY and nothing else. If there are notifications, rewrite each one in clean human Portuguese, concise but informative, and deliver them. Do not send silent confirmations. Do not explain empty scans. Do not invent status.\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 29th, 2026 — 12:15 (America/Sao_Paulo) / 2026-03-29 15:15 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774797302796}}
{"type":"message","id":"213cf0ea","parentId":"f06d46c4","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:15:05.143Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job asking me to:\n1. Read the README from task_watchdog\n2. Execute the watchdog.py script\n3. Parse JSON output\n4. If notifications is empty → reply EXACTLY \"NO_REPLY\" and nothing else\n5. If there are notifications → rewrite each in clean Portuguese, deliver them\n\nLet me start by reading the README to understand context.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01SPpFySrYAyvPD2nhcw2VsS","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":162,"cacheRead":15639,"cacheWrite":740,"totalTokens":16551,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0008100000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0015639000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.000925,"total":0.0033089000000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774797302922,"responseId":"msg_017YsnfdDPWnLwSywYeLDB1p"}}
